  "description": "Fix Card Display Issues on Documents Page\n\nResolve visual formatting problems with cards displayed on the documents page, including spacing, typography, and date localization.\n\nRequirements:\n- Add proper spacing/padding between card elements (margins, gaps between cards)\n- Fix internal card spacing (padding around content, gaps between text elements)\n- Improve text styling and typography for better readability (font sizes, weights, line heights)\n- Localize date formats from English to appropriate regional format\n- Ensure consistent card layout across all card instances on the page\n- Verify responsive behavior on different screen sizes\n- Check alignment and visual hierarchy of card content\n\nEdge Cases to Consider:\n- Cards with long text content that might wrap\n- Cards with missing optional fields\n- Different date formats needed (relative dates, full dates, time stamps)\n- Various content lengths across different cards",
